About
=====

This distribution includes petsc-2.3.1, slepc-2.3.1, arpack and libmesh from
CVS (November 13, 2006).

More uptodate scripts doing the same thing can be found in dftfem project (on
google).

Installation instructions:
==========================

cd
svn co http://libmeshpetscpackage.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ libmeshpetscpackage

wajig install g77 mpich-bin libmpich1.0-dev 
./buildarpack

wajig install refblas3-dev lapack3-dev
./buildpetsc

./buildslepc

./buildlibmesh
